    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Bubon galbaniferum are fever, which is reduced due to its antipyretic properties, and rheumatism, a condition alleviated by its anti-inflammatory compounds. Bubon galbaniferum has also been used to treat epilepsy, a neurological disorder caused by seizures, by regulating neurotransmitter activity. Its analgesic and anti-inflammatory properties make it effective in treating arthritis, a condition characterized by joint pain and inflammation. Additionally, Bubon galbaniferum has been employed in the treatment of skin conditions such as eczema, which is alleviated by its anti-allergic and anti-inflammatory compounds. By regulating the nervous system, Bubon galbaniferum helps in treating insomnia, a sleep disorder characterized by difficulty in falling asleep or staying asleep.",
